widestring_06AB53 `[TPL:0][TPL:A]Five days passed since we[N]entered the undersea[N]tunnel.[FIN][TPL:B]The scenery looks the same[N]no matter how much you[N]walk. We began to feel[N]overwhelmed…[FIN][CLD][PAU:28][TPL:6][TPL:9]Neil: How about we rest[N]here for today?[FIN][TPL:3][TPL:A][NAM:3]: I'm exhaaausted. I[N]think we walked about a[N]thousand kilometres today.[FIN][TPL:4][TPL:A][NAM:4]: Don't be stupid.[N]Human legs can't walk that[N]far.[FIN][TPL:1][TPL:A][NAM:1]: Geez, I can't stand[N]it…![FIN]This journey's been[N]nothing but one exhausting[N]event after another…[FIN][TPL:2][TPL:A][NAM:2]: Everybody's[N]thinking the same thing,[N]so be quiet…![FIN]More importantly, let's[N]eat. I'm hungry.[END]`

