widestring_06B57D `[TPL:2][TPL:9][NAM:2]: Humans are[N]mysterious, aren't we…?[FIN][TPL:12]When you're pushed to the[N]absolute limit, you might[N]know with a glance if[N]something is edible or if[N]it's poisonous.[FIN][CLD][TPL:2][TPL:A]I wonder if it was that[N]was for the people of the[N]past.[END]`

