widestring_06B86E `[TPL:0][TPL:A]We found these mushrooms[N]living in this tunnel when[N]we arrived.[FIN]They're our only source of[N]food.[FIN][TPL:B]Yesterday was fried[N]mushrooms. The day before[N]yesterday was boiled[N]mushrooms.[FIN]When we ate them raw three[N]days ago and they were[N]frightfully disgusting…[FIN]But we can't concern[N]ourselves with luxuries[N]like flavour.[FIN]We're being patient in[N]order to live, but when it[N]comes to having an empty[N]stomach…[END]`

widestring_06B0BC `[TPL:1][TPL:9][NAM:1]: Oh gosh. [NAM:0] found[N]mushrooms again…[FIN][TPL:2][TPL:B][NAM:2]: You have to think[N]of it as being better than[N]starving to death.[N]Alright, let's eat…[END]`

widestring_06AE88 `[TPL:0][TPL:9]Like this, one day again[N]passed slowly…[END]`

widestring_06B606 `[TPL:0][TPL:9]Eighth day since entering[N]the tunnel. [FIN][TPL:A]Unable to sleep, I was[N]staring at an underground[N]water stream…[END]`

widestring_06B661 `[TPL:2][TPL:8][NAM:2]: Can't sleep?[END]`

widestring_06B67B `[PAU:1E][TPL:0][TPL:A][NAM:0]: Yeah, it's because[N]I'm getting hungry.[N]…I'm kidding.[FIN][TPL:2][TPL:B][NAM:2]: Speaking of, [NAM:0].[N]As our journey continues,[N]we’ve changed a lot,[N]haven't we?[FIN]You could say that we've[N]matured somehow.[FIN][TPL:0][TPL:B][NAM:0]: I don't understand[N]it well myself, but…[FIN]I'm able to use mysterious[N]powers; you've seen me[N]transform into the form of[N]a warrior, right?[FIN]After the expedition with[N]my dad at the Tower of[N]Babel, my body had[N]changed.[FIN]I have a hunch that I'll[N]understand the secrets of[N]my power through this[N]journey.[FIN]By the way, [NAM:2], why[N]did you tag along in such[N]a dangerous journey?[FIN][TPL:2][TPL:B][NAM:2]: At first, it was[N]half for fun. But now it's[N]a private matter. Ehehe.[FIN]Since we won't be able to[N]avoid a lot of walking[N]tomorrow… I'll be going to[N]bed soon, okay?[END]`

widestring_06AD22 `[TPL:0][TPL:A]Two weeks since entering[N]the undersea tunnel. We[N]still can't see an exit…[END]`

widestring_06AD64 `[TPL:1][TPL:B][NAM:1]: Hey hey. Were there[N]eerie sounds coming from[N]above the tunnel when we[N]were sleeping last night?[FIN][TPL:4][NAM:4]: I think ya often[N]notice those sort o'[N]sounds… That ain't it; ya[N]were just gettin' tired.[END]`

widestring_06B10B `[TPL:1][TPL:B][NAM:1]: Listen… You can[N]hear it even now…! I[N]wonder what it is… That[N]sound…[END]`

widestring_06B13C `[TPL:3][TPL:9][NAM:3]: Could it be a[N]Leviathan…?[FIN][TPL:1][TPL:9][DLY:0][NAM:1]: This is bad…!![N]Run away!![FIN][TPL:2][TPL:A][NAM:2]: You can tell us to[N]run away, but where the[N]heck do we run to…!?[END]`

widestring_06B195 `[TPL:6][TPL:A]Neil: Everyone, be quiet…![N]This repeating vibration[N]sound…[FIN]This is Morse code…[FIN][TPL:B]When boats contact each[N]other, they use signals[N]where the length of sounds[N]map up to words.[FIN]I can try to decode a bit[N]of it, so please wait…[END]`

widestring_06B250 `[TPL:5][TPL:8][DLY:4]I'm [NAM:5]…[FIN][TPL:4][TPL:9][DLY:0][NAM:4]: Did ya say it's[N][NAM:5]?![FIN][TPL:2][TPL:9][DLY:0][NAM:2]: Shh… Be quiet…[N][PAU:3C][DLY:0]Neil's about to continue.[FIN][TPL:5][TPL:9][DLY:4]I was swallowed by a[N]Leviathan…[FIN][TPL:B]And then, when I regained[N]consciousness, my body had[N]been transformed into the[N]form of a Leviathan.[FIN]These life forms that we[N]call Leviathans may be[N]understood as humans that[N]live in the sea.[FIN]From what my fellow[N]Leviathans say, the light[N]of the comet distorts the[N]evolution of living things[N]or something like that.[FIN]I'd join you on your[N]journey again, but my[N]body's like this, so…[FIN]Please stay strong anyway,[N]and bring the mysteries of[N]the comet and the ruins to[N]light…[END]`

widestring_06B3EC `[TPL:6][TPL:9]Neil: I can't hear it[N]anymore…[FIN][TPL:1][TPL:9][NAM:1]: [NAM:5]… I pity him…[FIN][TPL:4][TPL:A][NAM:4]: Now that ya mention[N]it, I guess that guy must[N]have studied Morse code.[FIN][NAM:5] has learned[N]sophisticated things too,[N]hadn't he.[FIN][TPL:3][TPL:A][NAM:3]: But [NAM:5] no longer[N]is in human form…!![FIN][TPL:6][TPL:A]Neil: Nah, [NAM:3]. I don't[N]think you should assume[N]it's a bad thing.[FIN][TPL:B]We may only think that[N]the human body is the best[N]one because we're just[N]humans.[FIN]Alright. Keep your spirits[N]up and let's go ahead!![END]`
